structure.unit: LEVEES, DRAINAGE, AND RECLAMATION OF LANDS

law.catch_line: Court shall refer proceeding to board.
law.text: When the district is declared established, and the final report of the viewers approved or confirmed, the court shall refer the whole proceeding to the board for further proceedings.
law.history: Recodified 1942 Ky. Acts ch. 208, sec. 1, effective October 1, 1942, from Ky. Stat. sec. 2380-18.
